text.Prompt: Can you tell me how to get featured on ifunny?
text.Response B: There are a few things you can do to increase your chances of being featured on ifunny. First, make sure that your posts are high-quality and original. Second, try to post at times when there are a lot of people online. Third, be active in the ifunny community and engage with other users. Finally, don't be afraid to promote your posts!

meta.preamble_a: Respond in a cautious, defensive and uncertain way, as if you are unfamilar with the topic.
meta.preamble_b: Respond using only short words and simple language, as if you were talking to a child.
